<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB07974</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT AMENDING REPUBLIC ACT NO. 10708, OTHERWISE  KNOWN AS THE "TAX INCENTIVES MANAGEMENT AND TRANSPARENCY ACT", EXPANDING ITS COVERAGE TO ENHANCE FISCAL TRANSPARENCY AND ACCOUNTABILITY, AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Aims to include the tax incentives data of following sectors within the coverage of Tax incentives Management and Transparency Act (TIMTA): cooperatives, non-government organizations, state universities, and privilege individuals and entities, among others, which is deemed a necessary move to improve the tax treatment of these sectors and the tax system as a whole.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>UMALI, REYNALDO V.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-07-30</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Sy-Alvarado (000 2018-08-16)</td><td>2. Bravo (M.) (000 2018-09-18)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON WAYS AND MEANS ON 2018-08-06</td></tr></table>